  "description": "Motorsport command center: deep carbon-black surfaces, F1 racing red, silver detailing and checkered-flag dividers. Saira italic headings lean into the corner, Chivo Mono lap-timer figures keep the data honest. Flashy in the headers, ruthless legibility in the tables.",
